10. Governing Law

This Privacy Policy is governed by the laws of South Africa, without regard to its conflict of law principles.

By using the Amber app, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. Thank you for trusting Amber with your personal information. Your safety and privacy are our top priorities.
